p: Comes now the Grand Jury and by their foreman in the presence of the said Grand Jury present to the Court one indictment against Gus Bendjus Robert Stramlamt Ben Fredrickson, Frank Nelson Andrew Johnson, Leander Brown John Thompson, Alex Agren, Thomas Jacobs; for the Crime of Malicious Mischief which they say they find a true Bill in which twelve of them number concur which indictment is secured by the Court and by the Clerk duly filed in open Court in the presents of said Grand Jury
